user.intro:
Driven to create tech solutions that substantively and materially uplift the world.

Interested in electrical+nano+neuro engineering, ethical entrepreneurship, design, and public policy. Experienced with hardware and electrical engineering, as well as public speaking.

Working on an idea!
user.lookingFor: Learn about different sides of entrepreneurship and get to know more people building cool things.
